1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:01:01,980
[Episode 12]
[Your Love Came Too Late.]

15
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:06,860
I just intercepted a telegram
from the Sparks Society.

16
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:08,940
These rebels

17
00:01:10,620 --> 00:01:12,100
really lost their mind.

18
00:01:25,170 --> 00:01:29,220
[The nation-saving society
plans to kill Jiang Mohan.]

19
00:01:44,140 --> 00:01:45,460
I'll wait and see

20
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:48,700
who's coming to meet their demise.

21
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:10,420
What...

22
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:12,660
What are you doing?

23
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:15,620
I'm leaving.

24
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:17,100
I came to say goodbye.

25
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:19,980
Why?

26
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,940
Chihoko is jealous of me.

27
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:26,220
The Marshal suspects me.

28
00:02:26,940 --> 00:02:27,900
And you

29
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:30,020
are possessive about me,

30
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,780
yet you guard against my feelings.

31
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:34,780
I don't know
how I should behave around you.

32
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,300
Perhaps leaving

33
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:38,340
is a relief for both of us.

34
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:44,540
You can leave,

35
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,340
but not now.

36
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:49,060
I've been busy with work lately.

37
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:51,100
I hope you won't be a problem for me.

38
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:01,740
Let me do what I want one last time.

39
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:03,620
After this,

40
00:03:04,980 --> 00:03:06,620
I'll be on my own.

41
00:03:10,780 --> 00:03:12,580
If you don't want
to follow my footsteps,

42
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:15,100
then let me walk alone.

43
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:30,100
Come to Joys of Life when you're free.

44
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:32,340
There will always be a seat there

45
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:33,780
saved for you.

46
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:34,980
Stay.

47
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,420
Then...

48
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:39,460
♪Several springs have passed♪

49
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:41,380
In what capacity
are you asking me to stay?

50
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:42,970
♪The old garden causes tears♪

51
00:04:43,660 --> 00:04:44,580
Jiang Mohan.

52
00:04:44,930 --> 00:04:46,690
♪Leaning against the desk,
I overheard him♪

53
00:04:46,890 --> 00:04:50,310
♪Write and recite poems at night♪

54
00:04:52,810 --> 00:04:54,850
♪How could I forget you♪

55
00:04:55,010 --> 00:04:57,130
♪When I was lost and lonely♪

56
00:04:57,930 --> 00:04:59,930
♪I've finally heard about your life♪

57
00:05:01,050 --> 00:05:05,330
♪But years have gone by♪

58
00:05:06,490 --> 00:05:09,050
♪Many times,
I sighed about when you were born♪

59
00:05:09,370 --> 00:05:12,540
♪I was not yet born♪

60
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:19,580
♪Old memories stir up as I still wait♪

61
00:05:22,290 --> 00:05:25,970
♪It is a pity
that when you were born, I was not♪

62
00:05:26,210 --> 00:05:30,250
♪Szechuan Lovage grows as time goes on♪

63
00:05:30,610 --> 00:05:32,880
♪It is a pity that after we parted♪

64
00:05:33,030 --> 00:05:37,200
♪My thoughts grow thin
with petals falling♪

65
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:40,170
♪It is a pity
that when you were born, I was not♪

66
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:44,330
♪My heart is for one person♪

67
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:47,130
♪Tears fall like the rain♪

68
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:51,250
♪Strings are broken, words are silenced,
and the wind stops♪

69
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:09,420
Let's go home.

70
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:29,820
Sir,

71
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:33,020
you've been in a better mood lately.

72
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:34,500
Is it because of Miss Yu?

73
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:35,780
Don't ask dumb questions.

74
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,820
I'm just happy for you.

75
00:06:37,940 --> 00:06:39,060
All the things you've done for Miss Yu

76
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:40,060
behind her back

77
00:06:40,060 --> 00:06:41,340
are finally paying off.

78
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:42,260
Enough.

79
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:43,900
Keep those to yourself.

80
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:04,580
Where are you going

81
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:06,300
in this outfit?

82
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:08,820
I thought
we were going to a movie together.

83
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:15,380
Jiang.

84
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:18,860
Jiang.

85
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:21,620
Jiang,

86
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:22,580
I've just

87
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:24,220
killed a dozen of troublemakers.

88
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:26,420
Clean that up for me, will you?

89
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:28,180
I am very busy.

90
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:31,940
Yes, Marshal.

91
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:32,980
Let's go.

92
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:47,380
Well...

93
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:48,060
Go.

94
00:07:48,620 --> 00:07:49,420
I'll wait for you.

95
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:52,460
Okay.

96
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:54,740
Get the car ready.

97
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:55,540
Yes, sir.

98
00:08:25,780 --> 00:08:27,060
Yu,

99
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:29,340
this is thrilling.

100
00:08:29,340 --> 00:08:31,420
There's more to come.

101
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,460
You've got some nerve

102
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,860
to mess with my girl.

103
00:08:48,740 --> 00:08:49,980
Miss Yu...

104
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:52,100
Tell me

105
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:54,340
what the Military Governor
has done behind my back.

106
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:57,940
You... You heard it.

107
00:08:58,380 --> 00:09:00,300
But he won't let me tell you.

108
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:03,860
You have two options.

109
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:06,260
Either you die now

110
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:08,620
and I'll tell him

111
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:10,140
that you messed with my girl.

112
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:12,340
Or you tell me the truth

113
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,820
and I'll keep this as a secret.

114
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:16,420
If you really love Yu,

115
00:09:16,860 --> 00:09:18,540
I'll give you a generous dowry

116
00:09:18,860 --> 00:09:21,340
on your wedding day.

117
00:09:29,780 --> 00:09:31,820
Actually, the Military Governor

118
00:09:31,820 --> 00:09:33,220
is in deep love

119
00:09:34,060 --> 00:09:35,460
with you.

120
00:09:44,130 --> 00:09:45,210
[Zhongyi Hall]

121
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:49,780
Rest assured, sir.

122
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:51,580
Everything is in place.

123
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:56,260
If Qinghuan's life is at risk,

124
00:09:56,940 --> 00:09:58,420
wipe out the Qing Gang.

125
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:05,140
Sir, as you instructed,

126
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:07,780
Miss Yu's birthday gift and the restaurant

127
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:08,580
are all set up.

128
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:10,540
Good.

129
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:20,820
Lock down the entire city!

130
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:26,540
Well...

131
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:34,340
Sir,

132
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:38,220
there is something wrong with Yudie.

133
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:40,660
She's a spy
for the Japanese Chamber of Commerce.

134
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,740
[File: Yudie]

135
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:51,020
Placing spies around me

136
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,500
is like asking for death.

137
00:10:59,380 --> 00:11:00,300
Jiang Mohan,

138
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:02,620
what kind of person are you, really?

139
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:04,660
Even now,

140
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:06,700
I still can't see through you.

141
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:08,580
What's wrong?

142
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:10,260
Extra!

143
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:13,060
The bloodthirsty Military Governor
killed ten progressive youths!

144
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:14,580
Extra!

145
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:15,740
Stop the car.

146
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:17,580
...killed ten progressive youths!

147
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:21,460
Thank you.

148
00:11:26,570 --> 00:11:30,940
[Bloodthirsty Military Governor
Killed Ten Progressive Youths]

149
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:32,210
[Hideous Murderer]

150
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:35,780
Why do you have to be accused

151
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,820
while the Marshal killed these people?

152
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:41,540
Now that I'm labeled a hideous murderer,

153
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:45,060
it seems only fair to blame me

154
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,820
for every crime.

155
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:10,980
Sir,

156
00:12:11,500 --> 00:12:13,020
I feel there's something off.

157
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:19,100
Have our men on alert.

158
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:26,700
Mohan, I think we should go back.

159
00:12:29,820 --> 00:12:30,260
Let's go.

160
00:12:34,660 --> 00:12:35,340
Watch out!

161
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,140
Qinghuan!

162
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:39,940
Qinghuan.

163
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:41,500
I'm glad you're okay.

164
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:44,700
Go to the hospital!

165
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:46,900
Doctor!

166
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:47,580
Excuse me.

167
00:12:47,580 --> 00:12:48,100
Doctor!

168
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:49,580
She was shot.

169
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:50,420
Emergency room, now!

170
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:51,660
Inside. Hurry!

171
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:04,420
The bleeding won't stop. I'm afraid...

172
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:07,140
If anything happens to her,

173
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:08,700
I'll hold you all accountable.

174
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:11,060
Calm down. She's losing blood fast.

175
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:12,020
She needs a transfusion.

176
00:13:12,860 --> 00:13:13,620
Use my blood.

177
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:15,380
It's a match.

178
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,660
Take as much as you need.

179
00:13:17,060 --> 00:13:18,020
Don't worry about me.

180
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,180
Sir,

181
00:13:31,020 --> 00:13:33,340
you've been up for days over Miss Yu.

182
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:36,420
Even the toughest gets worn out.

183
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,100
Get out.

184
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:42,540
Have you caught the person?

185
00:13:44,260 --> 00:13:45,580
We've got a few suspects.

186
00:13:46,260 --> 00:13:47,380
I'll interrogate them myself.

187
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:48,740
Yes, sir.

188
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:57,940
Qinghuan.

189
00:13:59,780 --> 00:14:01,420
As long as you're safe and sound,

190
00:14:02,940 --> 00:14:04,620
I'll love you like no other.

191
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:06,340
♪The words once said will become scabs♪

192
00:14:06,340 --> 00:14:08,180
And I'll never push you away again.

193
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:11,900
♪Love hasn't etched itself
into gray hair♪

194
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:18,300
♪Yet that doesn't stop me
from gazing at you♪

195
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:26,580
♪Whose voice was crawling its way
into my dream♪

196
00:14:27,540 --> 00:14:30,220
♪I wake up to a quiet peace♪

197
00:14:31,260 --> 00:14:34,300
♪Time tells me to let go♪

198
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:37,940
♪I've waited for the spring rain
to evaporate in summer♪

199
00:14:38,780 --> 00:14:42,300
♪And autumn leaves to decay in winter♪

200
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:44,820
♪But I couldn't wait♪

201
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:46,220
♪For the flowers we planted together
to bloom in all four seasons♪

202
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:47,940
To gain his full trust,

203
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:49,660
I need you to work with me

204
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:51,620
to put on a show of me saving you.

205
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:53,460
♪I've waited for the sunset to fall
over mountains and turn into dusk♪

206
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:55,820
♪And the moon and stars to shift♪

207
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:57,020
Jiang Mohan,

208
00:14:57,940 --> 00:14:58,980
your affection has arrived

209
00:14:59,580 --> 00:15:01,260
upon a stage too late.

210
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:04,080
♪To weather the nights
and greet a fine day together♪

211
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:20,660
♪The waves♪

212
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:24,940
♪When will you stop
looking through them?♪

213
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:28,980
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

214
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:33,140
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

215
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:35,900
♪I thought you were an angel♪

216
00:15:35,980 --> 00:15:38,180
♪An angel who watched over me♪

217
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:41,260
♪And saw every side of me♪

218
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:43,900
♪Until reality is flooded♪

219
00:15:43,980 --> 00:15:46,140
♪You become sensible♪

220
00:15:46,220 --> 00:15:50,700
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

221
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:53,540
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

222
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:55,580
♪All clamoring because of you♪

223
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:57,660
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

224
00:15:57,820 --> 00:16:00,100
♪I cannot hear you♪

225
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:03,620
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

226
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:07,140
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

227
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:09,460
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

228
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:11,620
♪And thought there was ample time♪

229
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,660
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

230
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:15,740
♪But you always make me panic♪

231
00:16:15,820 --> 00:16:20,060
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

232
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:23,420
♪How much I am worth♪
